title: Atlas Shrugged: Who is John Galt? Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD]
description:
In theaters: September 12th, 2014

Description:

After 12 years of suffering mysterious disappearances of society's most-productive, the nation's economy is on the verge of collapse. In response, the government pursues policies imposing even greater brutality against those remaining. One man has the answer. One woman determined to keep the world running stands in his way. He swore by his life. She swore to stop him. Who is John Galt?

Director: James Manera

Writers: James Manera, Harmon Kaslow, John Aglialoro

Actors: Kristoffer Polaha, Laura Regan, Rob Morrow, Joaquim de Almeida, Eric Allan Kramer

Genre: Science Fiction, Drama

Run Time: 2 hours 18 minutes
